面向各自可能產生那些相關的影響？有那些需要再修改之處？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58fef3ea3170", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114040", "c": "302", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "就業安全制度", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "勞工行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-8b44517b-moex-00042', 'disabled-8b44517b', 'disabled-8b44517b-moex-114-1ffb5c63', 'sub-disabled-8b44517b-04', NULL, 'essay', '全球有關人工智慧（AI）在勞動市場中工作過程導入之發展是目前相當重
